data.description: This cute Ranch in lovely Bishop's Gate subdivision is waiting for its new owners! Featuring three bedrooms, 2 full baths (one off the master Bedroom) great location in a quiet neighborhood, close to all amenities, this home has an open floor plan for easy movement throughout the house as well as a bright sun-room for those winter months…. Leading out to a very private back deck surrounded by mature trees. a must see this will not last long.  Washer and Dryer hook up and 2 air condition window units available.. and a 2nd refrigerator in the basement.
